sequenceDiagram
    participant DeploySH as deploy.sh<br/>(Init Container)
    participant K8sAPI as OpenShift API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as rhods-operator<br/>(Watch Loop)
    participant Dashboard as rhods-dashboard<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NBC as odh-notebook-controller<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelCtrl as odh-model-controller<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant MMCtrl as modelmesh-controller<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DSPO as data-science-pipelines-operator<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant ClusterProm as prometheus-k8s<br/>(openshift-monitoring)<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant Blackbox as Blackbox Exporter<br/>9115/TCP HTTP
    participant AM as Alertmanager<br/>10443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PD as PagerDuty<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DMS as Dead Man's Snitch<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over DeploySH, K8sAPI: Flow 1: Deployer Bootstraps RHODS Platform

    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Create namespaces (oc apply)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>DeploySH: Created
    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Apply Dashboard CRDs<br/>(OdhApplication, OdhDocument, OdhQuickStart, OdhDashboardConfig)
    K8sAPI-->>DeploySH: Applied
    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Apply ISV app tiles, configs, serving runtimes
    K8sAPI-->>DeploySH: Applied
    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Create KfDef CRs (8 CRs)<br/>(dashboard, nbc, model-mesh, dspo, notebooks, monitoring, anaconda...)
    K8sAPI-->>DeploySH: Created
    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Apply NetworkPolicies, RBAC, ConsoleLink
    K8sAPI-->>DeploySH: Applied

    K8sAPI->>Operator: KfDef watch event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Deploy components from<br/>odh-manifests tarball
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Components deployed

    Note over Prom, DMS: Flow 2: Prometheus Monitoring Pipeline

    Prom->>ClusterProm: Federated scraping<br/>HTTPS/9091, TLS (service CA)<br/>Auth: Bearer token (SA)
    ClusterProm-->>Prom: haproxy, controller_runtime,<br/>container, kubelet metrics

    Prom->>Dashboard: Scrape metrics (via Blackbox)<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS
    Prom->>NBC: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP/8080, No Auth
    Prom->>ModelCtrl: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP/8080, No Auth
    Prom->>MMCtrl: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP/8080, No Auth
    Prom->>DSPO: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP/8080, No Auth

    Prom->>Blackbox: Probe request<br/>HTTP/9115
    Blackbox->>Dashboard: HTTP probe<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer token (SA)
    Dashboard-->>Blackbox: Probe result
    Blackbox-->>Prom: Probe metrics

    Note over Prom: SLO burn-rate evaluation<br/>(5m/1h, 30m/6h, 2h/1d, 6h/3d windows)

    Prom->>AM: Fire alert (burn rate exceeded)

    AM->>PD: Critical alert<br/>HTTPS/443, Service key<br/>(managed service only)
    AM->>DMS: Heartbeat webhook<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>(managed service only)
    AM-->>AM: Email via SMTP<br/>(user notifications)
